parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Roof Cover or Vinyl Roof Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the roof cover or vinyl roof can cause damage to the vehicle and potentially lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The roof cover or vinyl roof begins to rip off or falls off while driving
causing damage to the trunk lid or other vehicles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the paint job can lead to peeling, flaking, or deterioration of the paint, which can affect the appearance and resale value of the vehicle.
symptoms: The paint begins to peel off
flake
or deteriorate
revealing underlying layers or surfaces
and may cause damage to other parts of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to extended stopping distances, increased risk of accidents, and potential loss of control.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal travels further than usual
the vehicle takes longer to stop
the anti-lock brake light comes on
the brakes are hard to apply
and it may take both feet to stop the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear brake cylinder can cause the rear brakes to lock up, leading to loss of control, skidding, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The rear brakes lock up
fluid leakage from the brake cylinder
corrosion or gum formation on the drum brake pad.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to extended stopping distances, increased risk of accidents, and potential loss of control.
symptoms: The anti-lock brake light comes on
the brakes fail to engage properly
the vehicle takes longer to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure to Notify Owners of Recalls
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to notify owners of recalls can lead to unresolved safety issues, potentially causing accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Owners are not informed of recalls
owners are not notified of necessary repairs
owners are not reimbursed for repairs related to recalled components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tire blowouts can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Tires blow out while driving
loss of vehicle control
accidents
injuries.
